      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SNOWBALL ONE (2) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fifth (25.99) in a Bottom Up - Grade 5 at Warrnambool. Form here sound including six wins. Has a very good strike-rate from this draw, with three wins from six starts. Has ability and looks hard to stop. ARGYLE EMMA (7) had the drop on the lead early on but could only manage second, beaten 3 lengths (22.59) at Warrnambool in a Bottom Up - Grade 5 over 390m. Must be included in calculations. SWANKY CHIC (1) was prominent early from the tricky draw and did a fair job to be beaten 4 lengths into third (22.77) at this track in a Grade 5 over 390m. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Ready to find winning form. JACKPOT CASH (3) can measure up with the right run.",
